edu.nyu.cs.omnidroid.core
Class RegisteredApp

java.lang.Object
  edu.nyu.cs.omnidroid.core.RegisteredApp

public class RegisteredApp
extends java.lang.Object

RegisteredApps are applications that OmniDroid can interact with. These appplications are stored using the AGParser into a backend configuration file. This is an accessor method that provides an interface into each application's configuration.
